article.description: Quinton Johnson II came off the bench to score 19 points to lead Texas Rio Grande Valley to a 93-42 win over Howard Payne on Monday night.
article.headline: Texas Rio Grande Valley tops Howard Payne 93-42
article.linkText: Texas Rio Grande Valley tops Howard Payne 93-42
article.story: EDINBURG, Texas -- Quinton Johnson II came off the bench to score 19 points to lead Texas Rio Grande Valley to a 93-42 win over Howard Payne on Monday night. Johnson II hit 5 of 7 3-pointers. Jordan Jackson had 15 points for Texas Rio Grande Valley (1-1). Anthony Bratton added 10 points. Javon Levi had 10 points and 12 assists for the home team. Timothy Aguero had 15 points for Howard Payne, a Division III school. Jase Miguez added 13 points. Texas Rio Grande Valley plays North Dakota State on Friday. --- For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP-Top25 --- This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
